room_title: Escape room "Hotel California" by Element of Escape in Sarasota
room_address: 1007 Manatee Ave E Ste. A Bradenton, FL 34208
room_description: The hotel closed for unknown reasons in the 1930s and someone just purchased the untouched hotel. Your great grandfather was reporting on the hotel disappearances when he went missing himself many years ago. You are intrigued so you head in to investigate yourself. When you arrive they let you inside but they are set to knock the hotel down in one hour. Can you gather the evidence left behind by your grandfather and escape before the demolition is slated to begin?
